reviewText: So unimpressive I forgot I watched this video.
I love history programs, and I have watched quite a few since I joined Amazon Prime. We don't have cable so I use Amazon Prime daily, my wife also likes it for old T.V. shows and movies.

The subject was interesting enough and the price was reasonable for an hour documentary.  But I missed the critical information -- the running time was only 10 minutes, and the quality of the documentary was poor.  It was as if it had been done 60 years ago.  I cannot believe this is on the market.  A definite -- don't even think about buying it.
